com.apriori.possible

Interface Fulfillable<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of fulfilled value
    All Superinterfaces:
    Possible<T>

    public interface Fulfillable<T>
extends Possible<T>
    A possible value that can be set exactly once. Setting a value when not already present is called "fulfilling" the value.
